#: ../../install/tutorials/rpi.rst:59
msgid "Select your MicroSD card based on other people's experiences and technical benchmarks. For more information, read `this Community Forums thread <https://community.learningequality.org/t/microsd-cards-picking-the-right-one-experiences-and-benchmarks/935>`__."
